channel.title: Used to be port forworded~ then got a new comp
channel.description:
Ok I have made a server before and stuff, and i port forwarded too, but i have just got a new dell xp computer i threw away the old junky computer but i kept the router that was port forwarded, and i can get on to my server but no one else can.. I sware it's still forwarded, idk i have a belkin router..Every one used to be able to go onto my server but not since i got a new one.. Please reply ASAP.
Thanks, Heymon
Edit: anyone?
